{"ID":"20260605143843-5db665y","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605143843-5db665y","title":"2022年北京卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605143900-escp44u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-escp44u","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"病柏"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong sup","TextMarkTextContent":"1"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"】"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-fm233yg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-fm233yg","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杜甫"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-7z53jvi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-7z53jvi","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有柏生崇冈，童童状车盖。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-9u5u92a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-9u5u92a","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"偃蹇龙虎姿，主当风云会。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-ozwwku2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-ozwwku2","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"神明依正直，故老多再拜。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-jak3t63","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-jak3t63","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"岂知千年根，中路颜色坏"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【2】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-1p5017j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-1p5017j","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"出非不得地"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【3】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，蟠据亦高大。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-qoz9ffj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-qoz9ffj","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"岁寒忽无凭，日夜柯叶改。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-s94iv5n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-s94iv5n","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丹凤领九雏，哀鸣翔其外。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-w4rjpch","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-w4rjpch","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鸱鸮志意满"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【4】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，养子穿穴内。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-wuic22l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-wuic22l","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"客从何乡来，伫立久吁怪。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-x7vsmtt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-x7vsmtt","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静求元精理"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【5】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，浩荡难倚赖。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143900-ehq7g0s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143900-ehq7g0s","updated":"20260605143900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注释：【1】此诗作于上元二年（761）秋，杜甫时居成都草堂。【2】中路：中途。【3】出：生长。【4】鸱鸮：猫头鹰。【5】元精理：事物根本的道理。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143843-djtigb3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605143843-djtigb3","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-ukgl6yv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-ukgl6yv","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11．下列对诗句的分析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-pzzsbed","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-pzzsbed","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．前六句写柏树枝繁叶茂、高大轩昂之态，表现出诗人的赞美之情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-60kz2oc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-60kz2oc","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．“岂知”两句写柏的衰败，“岁寒”两句写凋零，流露出惋惜之情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-e9l89y6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-e9l89y6","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．“客从何乡来”两句，诗人由病柏而想到故乡，抒发了思乡之情。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-tw9oac4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-tw9oac4","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．这首诗在结尾两句抒发胸臆，表达了世事无常、难以意料的感慨。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-05bac9s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-05bac9s","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12．下列对这首诗的理解与赏析，正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-z76a1v9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-z76a1v9","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．诗人善用比兴手法，此诗中的病柏与刘禹锡“病树前头万木春”有相同的寄托。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-xkdns8a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-xkdns8a","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．文似看山不喜平，此诗运用转笔形成了诗意的转折，其色调也从明朗转为黯淡。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-zhj6i59","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-zhj6i59","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．杜甫借物抒怀，用柏树的“蟠据亦高大”之姿隐喻了当时藩镇的龙盘虎踞之势。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-397gtik","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-397gtik","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．此诗情感复杂而深沉，既有对现实的不满，也有对未来的希望，可谓沉郁顿挫。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143914-21w3a24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143914-21w3a24","updated":"20260605143914"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13．咏物诗注重通过意象表达主题，这首诗中的主要意象有哪些？分别说明这些意象有何意蕴。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143843-e219ogr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605143843-e219ogr","updated":"20260605143924"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605143924-emdvpkt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143924-emdvpkt","updated":"20260605143924"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11．C    12．B    13．①这首诗主要运用了病柏、丹凤、鸱鸮三种意象。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143924-eag7352","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143924-eag7352","updated":"20260605143924"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②病柏由盛而衰的变化，象征了唐朝从强盛到衰落的沧桑巨变；丹凤哀鸣，象征了正直之人被摈斥在外；鸱鸮意满，象征了奸佞小人盘踞于朝中。诗人借助这些意象表达了对国运时局的忧虑。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143843-p67nboy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605143843-p67nboy","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-3oob9bz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-3oob9bz","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11．本题考查学生分析理解诗歌内容的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-6kyj73d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-6kyj73d","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“诗人由病柏而想到故乡，抒发了思乡之情”错误，“客从何乡来，伫立久吁怪”两句是说，一个不知从哪里来的外乡人从此经过，久立于树前长吁讶然。他是感慨盛衰无常，不是思乡。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-s42erwb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-s42erwb","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-piutbsj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-piutbsj","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12．本题考查学生鉴赏诗歌表达技巧的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-00d6uae","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-00d6uae","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“有相同的寄托”错误，此诗以“病柏”为核心意象，通过描写“柏”之形象、际遇抒写人之命运、感慨，咏物抒怀，情感深沉。而刘禹锡“病树前头万木春”对世事的变迁和仕宦的升沉，表现出豁达、乐观的襟怀。寄托不同。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-f5gmol5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-f5gmol5","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“隐喻了当时藩镇的龙盘虎踞之势”错误，“蟠据亦高大”是形容衰时之柏，“得地”“盘据”承“千年根”，此柏不是所出非地，也不是生长浅薄，却变得枝枯叶燥，了无生机，隐喻家国衰落。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-67lj1vf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-67lj1vf","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.“也有对未来的希望”错误，全诗以“病柏”为核心意象，通过描写“柏”之形象、际遇抒写人之命运、感慨，咏物抒怀，表达盛衰无常的感慨。没有对未来的希望。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-1mpeqgd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-1mpeqgd","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-p2602b7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-p2602b7","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13．本题考查学生鉴赏诗歌事物形象和意蕴的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-ajglxxq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-ajglxxq","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这首诗主要运用了病柏、丹凤、鸱鸮三种意象。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-2cz8o85","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-2cz8o85","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“病柏”：“有柏生崇冈，童童状车盖。偃蹙龙虎姿，主当风云会”写柏的盛时，它“势尊严”，“状耸翠”，“干奇古”，“气阴森”，诗人用四句即生动地刻画出柏树的不凡。柏树的形象象征着强盛时的唐王朝。“岂知千年根，中路颜色坏”来了个“突转”，谁又能料到这植根深厚而悠远的“古柏，却半道变了“颜色”呢？于“王朝”而言就是衰落了。“岁寒忽无凭，日夜柯叶改”形容衰时之柏枝枯叶燥，了无生机。柏从繁盛到干枯象征唐朝从强盛到衰落。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-nwp5ms6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-nwp5ms6","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“丹凤”：“丹凤领九雏，哀鸣翔其外”因为大树将枯，“将九雏”的凤凰无枝可憩，只能上下盘旋，哀哀其鸣。丹凤哀鸣，象征了正直之人被摈斥在外。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-n8d3bgn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-n8d3bgn","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“鸱鸮”：“鸱鸮志意满，养子穿穴内”而对于恶鸟鸱鸮而言，则正中下怀，它们志得意满地率领众子孙穿穴打洞，立身其中。鸱鸮意满，象征了奸佞小人盘踞于朝中。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143941-24kpap2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143941-24kpap2","updated":"20260605143941"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这首咏物诗采用传统的比兴手法，有着强烈的象征色彩：它把国家比作一棵原本枝繁叶茂、现已病入膏肓的柏树，把能臣志士比作“哀翔其外”的凤凰，又把宵小之辈比作穿穴而居的恶鸟鸱鸮。"}]},{"ID":"20260605143843-t22r4mi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605143843-t22r4mi","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}